    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Correction</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of August 6 Correspondent's Report about detecting and disclosing water pollution at US beaches; Florida enacted law in June to provide comprehensive testing, beginning August 1, by coastal counties (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The Correspondent's Report column on Aug. 6, about detecting and disclosing water pollution at beaches in the United States, included an outdated reference to testing in Florida. A state law indeed exists; it was enacted in June to provide comprehensive testing by coastal counties, and participation in the program began on Aug. 1.</p>
      </block>
